text: Adolf Tannert (1 November 1875 - 30 January 1961) was a German gymnast. He competed in the men's individual all-around event at the 1900 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1875 births Category:1961 deaths Category:German male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Germany Category:Gymnasts at the 1900 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts from Berlin
